                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, G</hi> 44). I went with Turpin, on 27th Oct., to 53, Baldwin-street, City-road, and took the prisoner there—I searched the room in his presence, and found some duplicates in a box, in a pocket-book (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18481127-name-443" type="witnessName">
